some people say this
was the reason

576
01:07:59,960 --> 01:08:01,511
for the war in the first place.

577
01:08:04,035 --> 01:08:08,433
Anyway, it's the only
one that survived.

578
01:08:10,691 --> 01:08:12,665
How did you get it?

579
01:08:17,792 --> 01:08:22,383
They said that the war,
tore a hole in the sky.

580
01:08:22,384 --> 01:08:23,967
You probably
heard the stories.

581
01:08:23,968 --> 01:08:24,968
Yeah.

582
01:08:25,651 --> 01:08:29,948
Tore a hole in the sky,
sun came down,

583
01:08:29,949 --> 01:08:31,448
and burned everything.

584
01:08:32,014 --> 01:08:34,335
Everything and
everybody.

585
01:08:34,736 --> 01:08:36,843
You were lucky, to
hole up and hide in

586
01:08:36,844 --> 01:08:39,892
a place like this,
or underground.

587
01:08:41,819 --> 01:08:43,839
Most people weren't lucky.

588
01:08:47,231 --> 01:08:49,783
So, a year later we
started coming out.

589
01:08:50,746 --> 01:08:51,746
People wandering around.

590
01:08:53,461 --> 01:08:54,611
Not knowing what
I was going to do.

591
01:08:54,888 --> 01:08:58,821
Trying to find a place to survive.

592
01:08:59,362 --> 01:09:04,353
One day, I heard a voice.
It's hard to explain,

593
