700
01:17:10,896 --> 01:17:13,438
- Thank you for the tea.
- Thank you so much.

701
01:17:20,763 --> 01:17:22,174
Go back inside.

702
01:17:26,373 --> 01:17:27,345
George, what's wrong?

703
01:17:27,346 --> 01:17:29,827
A whole company of armed
degenerates, that’s what's wrong,

704
01:17:29,828 --> 01:17:32,247
