Fuck the china.

707
01:17:34,922 --> 01:17:36,409
Have you got any
more weapons?

708
01:17:36,410 --> 01:17:39,731
Weapons? I'll show
you some weapons.

709
01:17:46,567 --> 01:17:47,942
Come on.

710
01:17:47,943 --> 01:17:50,288
We know you're
in there.

711
01:17:51,383 --> 01:17:54,791
Come on out and nobody
needs to get hurt.

712
01:17:58,717 --> 01:18:00,923
I'll make it easy.

713
01:18:00,924 --> 01:18:03,909
Send out Solara
with the book.

714
01:18:03,910 --> 01:18:04,831
What are we going to do?

715
01:18:04,832 --> 01:18:06,629
I know what the
fuck I'm doing.

716
01:18:06,630 --> 01:18:08,220
Wait, wait.
-- That's all I want

