735
01:21:47,572 --> 01:21:48,874
It isn’t here.

736
01:21:51,811 --> 01:21:54,934
This is your last chance.
You give it up, or

737
01:21:54,935 --> 01:21:57,344
I swear I'll bury
you out here.

738
01:22:07,700 --> 01:22:11,705
Son-of-a...
Let's try this again.

739
01:22:16,035 --> 01:22:18,196
- Carnegie!
- What!?

740
01:22:28,049 --> 01:22:32,502
Now. Where's the book?

741
01:22:36,607 --> 01:22:39,233
Give him the book.
Please.

742
01:22:43,625 --> 01:22:45,554
Don't tell him.

743
01:22:55,113 --> 01:22:58,254
It's in the house.
Back of the TV.

744
01:22:59,587 --> 01:23:03,152
- Go check the TV.
- The what?

745
01:23:03,315 --> 01:23:04,551
You're fucking shitting me.

746
