What did I tell you?

755
01:25:26,439 --> 01:25:28,384
He's just a man.

756
01:25:31,599 --> 01:25:34,873
No! Leave him alone!

757
01:25:42,969 --> 01:25:45,423
Where's your protection now?

758
01:25:46,743 --> 01:25:48,143
Hmm?

759
01:26:00,255 --> 01:26:02,055
Pray for me.

760
01:26:05,283 --> 01:26:06,584
Okay?

761
