762
01:27:39,479 --> 01:27:40,779
Shit.

763
01:27:42,265 --> 01:27:43,565
Go back!

764
01:28:27,283 --> 01:28:29,738
Come on.
Come on!

765
01:29:28,400 --> 01:29:30,485
We've barely got enough
fuel to make it back.

766
01:29:30,526 --> 01:29:32,302
Do you want to
go after her?

767
01:29:34,177 --> 01:29:35,677
No.

768
01:30:56,539 --> 01:31:00,137
- Where are you going?
- I'm going West.

769
01:31:00,138 --> 01:31:00,938
Got to go West.

770
01:31:03,775 --> 01:31:05,075
Hey.

771
01:31:30,288 --> 01:31:34,156
- I'm sorry.
