777
01:31:46,022 --> 01:31:47,870
Did what I had to do.

778
01:31:47,871 --> 01:31:49,571
Didn't think anything
could make you

779
01:31:49,572 --> 01:31:50,272
give up that book.

780
01:31:56,366 --> 01:31:58,138
You know, for years
I've been carrying and

781
01:31:58,139 --> 01:32:00,024
reading it every day.

782
01:32:02,545 --> 01:32:05,529
I got so caught up
with keeping it safe

783
01:32:05,530 --> 01:32:10,408
