what I learned from it.

784
01:32:10,912 --> 01:32:12,823
Yeah? What's that?

785
01:32:13,899 --> 01:32:15,738
Just to...

786
01:32:18,151 --> 01:32:21,270
Do for others more than
you do for yourself.

787
01:32:23,659 --> 01:32:26,152
It's what I got
from it anyway.

788
01:33:12,907 --> 01:33:14,385
Do you smell that?

789
01:33:15,490 --> 01:33:18,908
- What?
